      "name": "Customer Service Sample Roleplay 10",
      "event": "Customer Service",
      "prompt": "Background: You are a customer service representative at a high-end electronics store. A client, Kai, purchased a pair of wireless headphones two months ago, and they recently stopped working. They are upset because the warranty states a replacement is only covered for manufacturing defects within the first 30 days. Kai insists they treated the headphones carefully and expects a free replacement.\n\nScenario: Your task is to: Calmly explain the store\u2019s warranty policy and how it applies to their situation. Offer alternative solutions, such as discounted repair services or applying a loyalty credit toward a replacement. Emphasize the importance of maintaining a positive relationship with them and ensuring customer satisfaction. OBJECTIVES OF THE ROLE PLAY The competitor must address the following during the role play: Interpret business policies to customers/clients Build and maintain relationships with customers Handle customer/client complaints Understands the techniques and strategies used to foster positive, ongoing relationships with customers Explain the role of ethics in customer relationship management",
