      "prompt": "Background: You are a marketing consultant hired by a local clothing brand looking to expand its online presence and increase sales. The brand currently operates out of one physical location and has a basic website but lacks a cohesive marketing strategy. They want to explore online advertising, social media promotion, and improve their e-commerce capabilities.\n\nScenario: Your task is to present a marketing plan that will help the brand improve its online visibility and increase both in-store and online sales. The client is particularly interested in understanding your approach to e-commerce, advertising strategies, and how you\u2019ll ensure ethical and legal marketing practices.\n\nObjectives: You must address the following during the role play: Describe how you will improve the brand's e-commerce platform to attract more online sales. Explain the channels of distribution you recommend for expanding both online and in-store sales. Outline your strategy for selecting appropriate promotion and advertising media for the brand. Discuss the legal and ethical considerations in online marketing and advertising. Explain how you will conduct marketing research to better understand the brand's target market.",
