        "Describe how you will configure internet resources to enable seamless communication and collaboration.",
        "Identify the key network resources and services needed for day-to-day operations.",
        "Discuss how the network will accommodate future growth and increased traffic.",
        "Explain the role of a network administrator in maintaining and troubleshooting the network."
